{
  "stem": "802.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm sure that they must have shot him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I cannot be sure 100%, but I am assuming that they must have shot him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he-- he-- and you know, he-- he revealed where our bunker was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a grenade was thrown in, or grenades.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they-- you know, the-- we all had to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- [SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then, in September, the large ghetto, as I recall and as I understand, was subdivided.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was divided further, into two parts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because most of the people had already been evacuated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'd been all, you know, sent to the gas chambers, to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mostly to Treblinka, most of the people from Warsaw, as far as I know, were sent to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And during that period, we were-- didn't-- we didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to go to this other part of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The one that became the small ghetto, part of the large ghetto that became the small-- small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was on [INAUDIBLE] street, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father thought that perhaps we ought to hide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't have the underground bunker yet at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had-- we were still hiding behind the-- the-- the door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we knew that it was too flimsy a hiding place, so it was useless.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was wondering whether or not we should go to where they were sending us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother made the ultimate decision.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My mother was often the decision maker, although they probably made decisions together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we did go that the other ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "By the time we reached it, there were corpses strewn all over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "People shot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were 1,200 people, something like this, were shot in one-- during one week.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we're stepping over the-- the-- the-- the bodies of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
